OL,3,CMurder in the street: The religious
OL,4,Cextremist's terror attack in Hartlepool
OL,6,FOn 15 October last year, Moroccan
OL,7,Fasylum seeker Ahmed Alid stabbed a
OL,8,Fpensioner six times in Hartlepool town
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FMinutes earlier and armed with two
OL,12,Fknives, at around 5am, he had broken
OL,13,Finto the bedroom of his housemate and
OL,14,Fhacked at him while he slept.
OL,16,FThe 45-year-old said he was inspired
OL,17,Fby "revenge" for the Israel-Hamas
OL,18,Fconflict.
