OL,4,Cextremist's terror attack in Hartlepool
OL,6,FAlid was convicted following trial of
OL,7,Fthe murder of Terence Carney and
OL,8,Fattempting to murder his housemate
OL,9,FJaved Nouri. He was also found guilty
OL,10,Fof assaulting two detectives.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced to on Friday 17 May.
OL,14,FThis is what happened.
OL,16,FOctober last year and the night-time
OL,17,Fpeace of Hartlepool's streets was
OL,18,Fabout to be shattered by hatred.
