OL,6,FA religious extremist living at a
OL,7,Fterraced property, shared by asylum
OL,8,Fseekers, chose the middle of the night
OL,9,Fto launch a sudden and murderous
OL,10,Frampage.
OL,12,F"Had it not been for the prompt
OL,13,Fresponse of Cleveland Police, I'm sure
OL,14,Fwe would have had more fatalities that
OL,15,Fday" - Paul Crowley, Cleveland Police
