OL,3,CMurder in the street: The religious
OL,4,Cextremist's terror attack in Hartlepool
OL,6,FAhmed Alid, an immigrant refused
OL,7,Fasylum in Germany after years of
OL,8,Fmoving between , decided to unleash a
OL,9,Fpunishment he later told police was
OL,10,Ffor the people of Gaza and what
OL,11,FBritain deserved for its support of
OL,12,FIsrael.
OL,14,FBeginning with one of his own
OL,15,Fhousemates, Javed Nouri, whose
OL,16,Fconversion to Christianity made him
OL,17,Fhis first target as he slept.
