OL,6,FBut the 45-year-old wanted more dead
OL,7,Fand a camera caught sight of him
OL,8,Fcrossing the street with his knife
OL,9,Fraised, searching for his next victim.
OL,11,FIt was 5am by now. The roads were
OL,12,Falmost empty. Closer towards the town
OL,13,Fcentre, 70-year-old grandfather
OL,14,FTerrence Carney was taking a regular
OL,15,Fearly morning walk.
OL,17,FCCTV captured him quietly crossing the
OL,18,Fstreet.
