OL,6,FComing the other way though was Alid,
OL,7,Fwho decided this "innocent old man",
OL,8,Fas he described, him would be next.
OL,10,FThe attack itself was brief. Alid's
OL,11,Fcries in Arabic of "God is great" rang
OL,12,Fout.
OL,14,FHis victim bled out and died just
OL,15,Fmetres from the town's police station
OL,16,Fthat he had been staggering towards.
OL,17,FThe Judge said Alid showed Mr Carney
OL,18,F"no mercy" and "left him on the road,"
OL,19,Fwhere he died.
