OL,3,CMurder in the street: The religious
OL,4,Cextremist's terror attack in Hartlepool
OL,6,FMr Carney suffered injuries to the
OL,7,Flung, liver, and heart, during the
OL,8,Fattack and was stabbed six times.
OL,10,FStill armed and moving further towards
OL,11,Fthe town centre, armed police brought
OL,12,FAlid's assault to an end, in just 20
OL,13,Fminutes. He was arrested with a knife
OL,14,Fpositioned in his waistband.
OL,16,FThe officers who apprehended him were
OL,17,Fpraised for their swift and safe
OL,18,Fcontainment of a suspect in
OL,19,Fcircumstances the region has never
OL,20,Fseen before - and for bringing him in
OL,21,Falive.
