OL,6,F"Instances like this don't routinely
OL,7,Ftake place in places like Hartlepool,
OL,8,For in the North East in general," a
OL,9,FCleveland Police representative told
OL,10,FITV Tyne Tees.
OL,12,F"We see news stories coming back from
OL,13,FLondon and all around the world, where
OL,14,Fwe have incidents of a terrorist
OL,15,Fnature where the suspect is shot and
OL,16,Fkilled. But we need to be seen to be
OL,17,Fbringing people to justice.
