OL,8,Fwould have killed thousands".
OL,10,FDuring the interview, Alid became
OL,11,F"irritated" with the interpreter, Mrs
OL,12,FJustice Cheema-Grubb said.
OL,14,FShe told the court how after that
OL,15,Finterview, Alid , preventing the
OL,16,Fofficers from opening it.
