OL,3,CMurder in the street: The religious
OL,4,Cextremist's terror attack in Hartlepool
OL,6,F"His solicitor was so concerned, he
OL,7,Fmade an emergency call from inside the
OL,8,Froom. When the door was opened from
OL,9,Fthe outside, the defendant lunged at
OL,10,Ftwo female interviewing officers, and
OL,11,Fhe refused to release her.
OL,13,F"The other officer tried to separate
OL,14,Fthem. All three fell to the floor. The
OL,15,Fofficers were shaken, and one suffered
OL,16,Fmodest injury."
OL,18,FAlid was charged the following day on
OL,19,F16 October 2023.
