OL,3,CMurder in the street: The religious
OL,4,Cextremist's terror attack in Hartlepool
OL,6,FThis lone operator carried out what he
OL,7,Fcalled his "raid", classed as part of
OL,8,Fan increasing threat that is hard to
OL,9,Fspot and even harder to stop before it
OL,10,Fis too late.
OL,12,FDr Tarela Ike, Senior Lecturer in
OL,13,FCriminology and Policing at Teesside
OL,14,FUniversity told ITV Tyne Tees: "A lone
OL,15,Foperator, operates in isolation. They
OL,16,Fare solitary in nature, which makes it
OL,17,Fdifficult to counter because they
OL,18,Fdon't speak to people about it.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/16
