OL,6,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb said he had
OL,7,Fwaited to assault Mr Nouri when he was
OL,8,F"asleep and vulnerable," and that "the
OL,9,Flife he had started to build in this
OL,10,Fcountry was shattered by what
OL,11,Fhappened".
OL,13,FThe judge then said Alid "attacked an
OL,14,Funarmed and elderly man who was unable
OL,15,Fto defend himself".
